Generalization of criteria
\[
\tr[\rho_{A,Q}^n(t)] = \int_{-\pi}^{\pi} \frac{d\vb*{\alpha}}{(2\pi)^{n-1}}  
\underbrace{\delta_p\left(\sum_{j=1}^n \alpha_j\right)}_{\text{Dirac delta function}}
\underbrace{\tr\left[\prod_{j=1}^n \rho_A(t) e^{i\alpha_j Q_A}\right]}_{\text{charged moments}}
\]


\(\Pi_q = \frac{1}{2\pi} \int_{-\pi}^{\pi} d\alpha e^{i\alpha(Q_A - q)}\)
